name: Burgundy Text Dip Dye Fade ~ Obscenity
description:
This is the first of many designs for ObscenityApparel!

The Tee shown in the photo is a Medium, unfortunately only available in sizes Medium and Large and both in small quantities for the first ever order. It is also 100% Cotton.

NOTE: Your item will be dispatched within 2-3 Working days.

Please read before ordering: Some Dip dye effects will be different to the one shown as they are dyed by hand and very hard to get the same way every time. There may be some dye on a sleeve or near the top where the Tees are dyed several at a time. Also the text on the Tee doesn't look the way it does in the picture, in person it is a flat black, the light is just hitting it funny here. 

When washing this Tee it is best to use a colour catcher or wash darks seperatly as the dye can run and ruin some clothes
